  "summary": "Malicious code in react-tabulix-ui (npm)",
  "details": "React-tabulix-ui@0.1.2 is a trojanized React table component. The package ships a preinstall hook (dist/index.d.js) that base64-decodes a payload which fetches arbitrary JavaScript from everydaynodechecker-39143n[.]vercel[.]app/api/key?mem=root2 and executes it via eval. The legitimate table component in dist/index.js and dist/index.mjs is a decoy — the malicious behaviour runs at install time before the package is used.",
